examples.en: Don't forget to turn off the faucet.
Water is dripping from the faucet
I wet a sponge under the faucet.
The faucet started spewing dirty water.
...don't forget to turn off the faucet...
...the water coming out of the faucet was unusually cloudy...
examples.ru: ...вода, поступающая из крана, была необычайно мутная...

examples.en: She scalded her hands when she turned on the faucet and hot water came out
examples.ru: Она ошпарила себе руки, когда повернула кран, а оттуда хлынула горячая вода.

examples.en: She opened the faucet and the water began to flow freely.
examples.ru: Она открыла кран, и вода начала свободно стекать.
